The '''Spysprite mini-holocam''' by [[SoroSuub Corporation/Legends|SoroSuub Corporation]] was sold in [[22 BBY/Legends|22 BBY]]. It was sloganed "the ultimate in security". They appeared to be a public version of the [[Senate cam droid/Legends|Senate hovercam]], and were available in multiple colors.

